# GTMC

O Grupo de Teoria de Materia Condensada pertence ao departamento de fisica da UFC 
e reune neste repositorio documentacao e softwares relacionados as suas linhas de pesquisa.

### Graduacao/Pos

* [Feynmann Lectures on Physics](https://www.feynmanlectures.caltech.edu/)
* [Audio from Feynmann Lectures on Physics](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1HgfLFwafPKNCt1VbjvqBxN4dc9irQTka?usp=sharing)
* [Quantum Mechanics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1VUE3SREqYWfojhYRDr4GVDm6lQ6X9bMu) by Landau
* [Introduction to Quantum Mechanics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1d6molE5K2XLY7IRah8xTCT50LRVrNn1C) by David J. Griffiths
* [Introduction to Electrodynamics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1wteP3RArWnDchKF_9dI6qYb1uGvbdN4G) by David J. Griffiths
* [Classical Electrodynamics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1oJMbIgMWvPp0quuMb379DS_TQvBMXMKc) by Jackson
* [Modern Quantum Mechanics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1_c6GYbEZImXqWl6fh5tSXCNYp2CEEg4m) by Sakurai
   
### Teoria de muitos corpos

* [Quantum Theory of Many-Particle Systems](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1RGbeWpYXFb5FRRKnUKG_96bP7SLmaK66) by Fetter and Walecka
* [A guide to Feynman Diagrams in the Many-Body Problem](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Lz3whL2RDeRqHVjl_ffbN_pVuflLrFhm) by Mattuck

### Fisica do estado solido

* [Solid State Physics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ElBcCEB0FWfYbftX8BRBZnNXmq9QxHXd) by Giuseppe Grosso
* [Solid State Physics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=11R4AvNFRjiT05EKBBFb-Ya8Yz50HgOnB) by Ashcroft
* [Fundamentals of the Physics of Solids V. I, II, III](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ZHmmfaM5zpLnTIMxDewCnx_iocmgd7yy) by Jelo Solyom

### Optoelectronics

* [Quantum Theory of Optical and Electronic Properties of Semiconductors](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pAtNBCi2DSW55QrahTjpBrBaXHzxc8jO/view?usp=sharing) by Hartmug Haug
* [An Introduction to Graphene Plasmonics](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1R4QsX7O_LwXeD2VwfAjn4gvRx_fFnQw8) by Nuno Peres

### DFT

* [Electronic Structure Calculations for Solids and Molecules](https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B6X9uEKN4qXlOFlES2E3Mjh1VEU/view?usp=sharing) by Jorge Kohanoff

### DTU

* [CAMD Summer School 2018 (slides and audio)](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1QQeXO3smU_eLC89ng-iB2GFhJzt22J-w)
* [Advanced Solid States Physics (slides, problems and notes)](https://drive.google.com/open?id=17lTLU4GlZUM1Rp1wcH4Fspg3rsKr9ONU) by Kristian Thygesen
* [Electronic Structure Methods (Theory exercises, slides and journal club)](https://drive.google.com/open?id=1KOXR1BNED48n46zwNODG_7OMNgZeS0SC) by Kristian Thygesen

